summary.label:
We all have busy lives. The SQE1  Exam Revision App allows you to revise on the go, while you travel to work or wait for a friend in a coffee shop.

This app contains up to date questions similar to the SQE1  Exam Revision App designed by the Solicitors Regulation Authority.

Our app has the ability to offer instant feedback and a final percentage score after every 10 questions completed.

In the SYLLABUS section, the user has the option to select a specific section of the exam to revise, like:

Business Law and Practice;
Dispute Resolution; 
Contract;
Tort; 
Legal System of England and Wales; 
Constitutional and Administrative Law and EU Law and Legal Services. 
Property Practice; Wills and the Administration of Estates; Solicitors Accounts; Land
Law; 
Trusts;
Criminal Law and Practice.

In the PROGRESS section, the app will show you how much time you spent preparing for the exam and the progress that you are making.

The TARGET section is designed to help you revise the questions answered wrong the first time, so you can increase the final score. The app is available to use offline, once downloaded.

Are you finding it hard to set a time for revision?

Our app will remind you to revise every day if you set it and can send you a Question of the day as a notification every morning.

With all of these great ways to revise, it is almost impossible not to pass the test.

This app is regularly updated and new questions are added with each update.


Disclaimer:
The questions in this app are similar to the ones created by the Solicitors Regulation Authority, however, the Solicitors Regulation Authority did not endorse this app and should not be associated with it.
